library(tidyverse)
myurl <- "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/reisanar/datasets/master/all_grammy.csv"
data <- read_csv(myurl)

 Column specification 
cols(
  .default = col_character(),
  danceability = col_double(),
  energy = col_double(),
  loudness = col_double(),
  speechiness = col_double(),
  acousticness = col_double(),
  instrumentalness = col_double(),
  liveness = col_double(),
  valence = col_double(),
  tempo = col_double(),
  duration_ms = col_double(),
  time_signature = col_double()
)
 Use `spec()` for the full column specifications.

sumdata <- data %>%
  select(!c(playlist_img, album_img, track_uri))
